  "description": "Apple Health per-source view. Primary panels query the Unified* measurements filtered to Source='Apple' (one series per metric, de-duplicated across Apple devices via the importer's priority pick). The Workouts table reads raw AppleHealthWorkout for per-workout detail. Raw AppleHealth* per-device measurements are preserved in InfluxDB for ad-hoc audit queries \u2014 see docs/apple-health-import.md.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
